# MEDICAL CORE POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: medical
scope: medical.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines policy constraints for medical.

## policy_rules
Medical policy constrains:
- who may observe, assess, intervene, or review
- what medical detail may be disclosed
- when medical paths must be denied or escalated

## required_behavior
- intervention scope must be explicit
- disclosure scope must be explicit
- denial behavior must be explicit

## disclosure_matrix
- bounded public medical summary
- actor-scoped detail
- operator/reviewer detail
- historical medical detail
- denied output

## allowed_denied_matrix
- allow medical action only for valid scope
- allow disclosure only for allowed actors
- deny hidden widening of medical authority
- deny disclosure beyond allowed scope
